Join EECS Women's History Month for our Industry Office Hours THIS WEEK!


- [3/10 @ 4:30 PM PT] Human Capital Industry Office Hours: https://www.facebook.com/events/188350852719281
- [3/10 @ 5:30 PM PT] Ambidextrous AI Industry Office Hours:  https://www.facebook.com/events/437969797476836
- [3/11@ 12 PM PT] Atlassian Industry Office Hours: https://www.facebook.com/events/708015116532369
- [3/11@ 5 PM PT] Texas Instruments Industry Office Hours: https://www.facebook.com/events/923032858470046/


Industry Office Hours are drop-in events where you can meet recruiters and engineers from different companies, learn more about internship and full-time opportunities, review your resume, and more! Signups are linked on each Facebook event! Events are open to all students! 

Want to learn more about EECS Women's History Month?  Head over to our Calendar at https://www.eecswhm.com and join our discord at https://tinyurl.com/eecswhm2021 to join the fun!
history.subject: Join EECS Women's History Month Recruiting Events!
